javelin.model.world.location.town.research

Class Research

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.view.screen.Option
      • javelin.model.world.location.town.research.Research
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccommodationResearch, Grow, ItemResearch, LairResearch, Recruit, SpecialResearchCard, TransportResearch, UpgradeResearch

    public abstract class Research
extends Option
    Represents a way in which a Town can be improved. It's a "card-game" mini-game so each town draw(Town) cards and has to use one before drawing another.
    Author:
    alex
    See Also:
    ResearchData, Serialized Form
